    <exercise>
    <title>Legalization of marijuana, mathematical interval</title>
    <statement>
      <p>The General Social Survey asked a random sample of 1,563 US adults: <q>Do you think the use of marijuana should be made legal, or not?</q> 60% of the respondents said it should be made legal. <xref ref="data:gssgrass" /></p>
